stage : 

 - to stage a file is simply to prepare if finely for a commit.
 
 - Stage is the step before to make a commit, you add modified files to "Staged files" to create your next commit.
 
stash :

 - stash will move your modified files into a stack.
 
 - so, later in the same or in another branch, you will be able to bring them back and see those modifications in your project.
